OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Flooks mainly dry with a few clear
OL,7,Fintervals. Cloud will increase
OL,8,Fovernight with some patchy rain
OL,9,Flikely. Clearer spells and dry
OL,10,Fconditions returning through the early
OL,11,Fhours.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FEarly sunshine will give way
OL,14,Fto thickening cloud and outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain on Saturday morning, accompanied
OL,16,Fby fairly brisk winds. A breezy and
OL,17,Fshowery afternoon will follow.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
