OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,6,Fwill be a fresher, still breezy day
OL,7,Fwith sunshine and scattered showers.
OL,8,FStaying more changeable than of late
OL,9,Finto early next week. Some sunshine,
OL,10,Fthough rain at times too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
